(793, 39, 'E-00708', '', 17, 'Gucci Flora Gorgeous Gardenia Intense, 100ml, eau de parfum', '648581006-a9b11e51e1cb0c2a025b1e0531773e1b-photo_2025-10-30_22-30-30.jpg', 190, '$', 100, 'Celebrating the gardenia flower that inspired the original scent, Gucci Flora Gorgeous Gardenia Intense Eau de Parfum is the most concentrated fragrance in the Gucci Flora collection. This new interpretation reveals a floral and enchanting woody heart. The fragrance opens with bright Italian Mandarin, unfolding into a fresh bouquet of Gardenia Accord and Hedione. Vibrant green notes add energy, while Sandalwood brings warmth and depth. The long-lasting fragrance is perfect for infusing any moment with a sensation of pure bliss.', '‡∏™‡πà‡∏á‡∏ü‡∏£‡∏µ', 0, '2025-10-30 14:31:22'),
