(799, 39, 'E-00714', '', 17, 'Mascara Le Magn&eacute;tisme, black', '993203133-8cf3a58cfefbb4ae1dc933ae0f3786d5-photo_2025-10-30_22-42-45.jpg', 36, '$', 300, 'With a creamy and lightweight texture, Gucci&#039;s Mascara Le Magn&eacute;tisme delivers impressive volume and curl, creating a captivating fan-effect. Its comfortable and intense black formula lifts the lashes with high definition and separation. Encased in a sleek black tube paired with a gold-toned wand, the mascara is decorated with a gold-toned Gucci logo, making it a true object of desire.', '‡∏™‡πà‡∏á‡∏ü‡∏£‡∏µ', 0, '2025-10-30 14:43:23'),
